 The other day, Fred Wilson sent out a short tweet storm turned post on determining if an entrepreneur's startup idea is a good one. It's short. Take a minute to read it over.  At its core, the post and the comments talk about belief in an idea and it got me thinking about some things as an educator.  Tweet 7:   and you have to believe in yourself and your idea or nobody else ever will